":1064,"filename":3738,"description":3739,"750x750px":94,"160x90px":94,"365x225px":94,"100x100px":94,"760xautopx":94,"1200x675px":94,"gallery_id":3711},5368598,"https://storage.googleapis.com/poludniowaoficyna-pbem/galleries/4b84ed67-8e89-4b6a-95cf-696639571409","2026-03-10 10:30:55","4b84ed67-8e89-4b6a-95cf-696639571409","\u003Cp>Sukces to nie tylko talent, ale przede wszystkim setki godzin ćwiczeń i dbałość o każdy detal &ndash; od techniki strzyżenia, przez dob&oacute;r kosmetyk&oacute;w, aż po końcową stylizację\u003C/p>",{"id":3741,"name":97,"url":3742,"thumbnail":3742,"created_at":3743,"tags":97,"author":3708,"type":1064,"filename":3744,"description":3745,"750x750px":94,"160x90px":94,"365x225px":94,"100x100px":94,"760xautopx":94,"1200x675px":94,"gallery_id":3711},5368610,"https://storage.googleapis.com/poludniowaoficyna-pbem/galleries/e3c3198d-0ddd-4a95-847d-665bba2e7280","2026-03-10 10:30:57","e3c3198d-0ddd-4a95-847d-665bba2e7280","\u003Cp>Warto dodać, że w sukcesie sw&oacute;j udział miał r&oacute;wnież Kamil Druciarek, kt&oacute;ry jako model wykazał się profesjonalizmem, pozwalając uczennicom zaprezentować pełnię ich umiejętności\u003C/p>",{"id":3747,"name":97,"url":3748,"thumbnail":3748,"created_at":3749,"tags":97,"author":3708,"type":1064,"filename":3750,"description":97,"750x750px":94,"160x90px":94,"365x225px":94,"100x100px":94,"760xautopx":94,"1200x675px":94,"gallery_id":3711},5368592,"https://storage.googleapis.com/poludniowaoficyna-pbem/galleries/7c00b7ba-2051-430a-bfd1-dc7e4bf55fd8","2026-03-10 10:30:54","7c00b7ba-2051-430a-bfd1-dc7e4bf55fd8",{"id":3752,"name":97,"url":3753,"thumbnail":3753,"created_at":3754,"tags":97,"author":3708,"type":1064,"filename":3755,"description":97,"750x750px":94,"160x90px":94,"365x225px":94,"100x100px":94,"760xautopx":94,"1200x675px":94,"gallery_id":3711},5368604,"https://storage.googleapis.com/poludniowaoficyna-pbem/galleries/2fdf9bed-dcd5-4778-afdf-6108d53414f8","2026-03-10 10:30:56","2fdf9bed-dcd5-4778-afdf-6108d53414