ane z Programem Ochrony Ludności i Obrony Cywilnej, odnosili sukcesy sportowe, organizowali szkolenia i ćwiczenia.",{"title":3986,"description":3987,"keywords":3988,"fb_cover":3989,"fb_title":94,"fb_description":94},"Trudny, ale dobry rok. Narada roczna w pleszewskiej komendzie","Ponad 670 razy interweniowali pleszewscy strażacy w 2025 roku. Najwięcej akcji - 309 - odnotowano na terenie miasta i gminy Pleszew, najmniej - 38 - w Choczu. Oprócz standardowych działań, realizowali zadania związane z Programem Ochrony Ludności i Obrony Cywilnej, odnosili sukcesy sportowe, organizowali szkolenia i ćwiczenia.","kp psp pleszew, straż pożarna podsumowanie 2025 roku",{"value":3990},{"filename":94,"name":94,"tags":94,"thumbnail":94,"type":94,"url":94},"2026-03-10 13:22:11","https://zpleszewa.pl/wiadomosci/trudny-ale-dobry-rok-narada-roczna-w-pleszewskiej-komendzie/0N5UjC9ENjNlLMbdlvBA","trudny-ale-dobry-rok-narada-roczna-w-pleszewskiej-komendzie","Setki interwencji i nowe wyzwania. Za strażakami trudny, ale dobry rok",[2871,3996],"straż pożarna podsumowanie 2025 roku",[3998,3999],{"tag":2871,"slug":2877},{"tag":3996,"slug":4000},"straz-pozarna-podsumowanie-2025-roku","2026-03-11 10:48:36",["Reactive",4003],{"ads":9,"aid":4004,"alternative_gallery_style":9,"attachments":4005,"author":4019,"author_info":13,"category":4020,"comments":9,"comments_auth":9,"content":97,"created_by":2519,"created_by_name":97,"custom_html":94,"featured":13,"gallery_ads":4021,"gallery_picked":55,"id":4022,"is_advertisement":13,"is_photostory":13,"is_pool":13,"multiportal":94,"view_type":94,"is_redirect":13,"keywords":4023,"lead":4031,"locked":13,"meta":4032,"parent_domain":2543,"parent_id":4038,"photostory_added":55,"pool_picked":94,"pool_under_photostory":55,"premium":13,"published":22,"published_at":4039,"quiz_picked":94,"recommended":13,"redirect_url":4037,"self_url":4040,"show_quiz_cover":55,"slug":4041,"sponsored":55,"short_title":4042,"tags":4043,"tagsRaw":4047,"title":4033,"type":1108,"uid":4022